le results in our brain imaging\nproblem, since it allows the discrimination between active and inactive\nregions, while at the same time ranking the discoveries into clusters\nrepresenting tiers of similar importance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jun 2021 16:46:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 23:29:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 27 Jan 2023 08:20:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-30"}
