tly governed by local interactions of the isotherms. It is found that\nenhancement in $\\widetilde{S_d}$ in regions of large negative curvature occurs\nas a result of these interactions, evincing that the interaction model is\nuseful for high $Ka$ turbulent premixed flames as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jun 2021 20:01:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-03"}
