oretical calculations lend further\nsupport that the phase transition and the corresponding gap opening in\nTa$_2$NiSe$_5$ is largely structural by nature with possible minor contribution\nfrom the putative exciton condensate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jun 2021 22:20:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-30"}
